title: The COMPLETE Marceline the Vampire Queen: Adventure Time Timeline

media:group.media:title: The COMPLETE Marceline the Vampire Queen: Adventure Time Timeline
media:group.media:description:
In this video we look at the entire timeline of Marceline the Vampire Queen from Adventure Time. Voiced by Olivia Olson, and aired on the Cartoon Network, we look at Marceline's complete history, her past and future. I've put Marceline's life in chronological order. From season 1 to Adventure Time Distant Lands. I go into her friendship with Finn and Jake, as well as her romance with Princess Bubblegum.
This video also explores his rivalry and friendship with the Ice King.
So come along with me as I go into the complete history of Adventure Time.
